25 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Excess revenue -- rebate to policyholders and certificate holders.
26 (1) (a) (i) A dental insurer that issues, sells, or renews a plan, policy, contract, or certificate covering dental
27 services shall provide an annual rebate or credit to each policyholder or certificate holder:
28 (A) whether individual or part of a group;
